&lt;p&gt;First of all, I would like to thank all of our customers for supporting EvoBurst Solutions over the 8 Months, there have been some great times, as well as some issues with nodes etc. &lt;br /&gt;But in the process of all this, we have managed to upgrade most of our servers to provide better service for all.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;With the pending completion of our Custom Control Panel drawing closer, we have been in contact with a number of providers to supply a great product with multiple Dedicated IP Addresses for a great price. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;EvoBurst LA - rDNS Services are now active on both IPv4 + IPv6. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We also would like to put out some new offers aimed at our EvoBurst &amp;amp; BudgetVZ Brands available until 15/06/2015!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #008000;"&gt;We have also changed the features on one of our more popular EvoBurst plans!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
